data.description: Endless opportunities to make this one in Aulander your own! Large backyard, lot is just over half an acre. The large family room and bedrooms feature vaulted ceilings with exposed beams. The upstairs loft area could be used as a third bedroom or additional living space. Pull down attic stairs lead you to a fully floored attic, great for storage! Electrical panel in the detached garage.
